= rrrcov aka Rcov on Ruby on Rails

Rcov on Ruby on Rails is a Rake task which accurately reports code coverage 
for a typical Ruby on Rails project.

 1. Install rcov from http://eigenclass.org/hiki/rcov
 
 2. Install rrrcov from Subversion http://svn.openrain.com/rails/rrrcov

 3. To test like a pirate, run rake test:rcov

